        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;stateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --&gt; PendingFill: 进入预测房价业务\n\n    state \&quot;待填写&lt;br/&gt;────────&lt;br/&gt;do / 填写房源特征\&quot; as PendingFill\n    state \&quot;待检查&lt;br/&gt;────────&lt;br/&gt;do / 检查信息完整性&lt;br/&gt;do / 检查信息合理性\&quot; as PendingCheck\n    state \&quot;待补充&lt;br/&gt;────────&lt;br/&gt;do / 补充房源特征&lt;br/&gt;do / 修改房源特征\&quot; as PendingSupplement\n    state \&quot;可评估&lt;br/&gt;────────&lt;br/&gt;do / 形成参考价格&lt;br/&gt;do / 生成结果说明\&quot; as Assessable\n    state \&quot;已反馈\&quot; as Feedbacked\n    state \&quot;不可评估&lt;br/&gt;────────&lt;br/&gt;do / 说明不可评估原因\&quot; as Unassessable\n\n    PendingFill --&gt; PendingCheck: 提交预测请求\n\n    PendingCheck --&gt; PendingSupplement: 信息缺失或不合理\n    PendingSupplement --&gt; PendingCheck: 修改后重新提交\n\n    PendingCheck --&gt; Assessable: 信息完整且合理\n    Assessable --&gt; Feedbacked: 预测结果已展示给用户\n    Feedbacked --&gt; [*]: 用户查看结果，结束本次预测\n\n    PendingCheck --&gt; Unassessable: 评估条件不满足\n    Unassessable --&gt; [*]: 结束本次请求&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="Rat4t0W0rzK5mIXzTLp2-106">
          <mxCell connectable="0" parent="1" style="group;transparentBounds=1;editIcon=1;lockedGroup=1;groupPadding=20;" vertex="1">
